<title>USA: Service Corp sees $42 mln gain in Q1.</title>
<headline>Service Corp sees $42 mln gain in Q1.</headline>
<dateline>HOUSTON 1997-02-18</dateline>
<text>
<p>Service Corp International said it received $148 million in proceeds from the sale of 7,994,000 shares of Equity Corp International, resulting in an after-tax gain of $42 million, which will be posted in its first quarter financial results.</p>
<p>On February 5, Equity Corp said it had completed a public offering of common stock, which included the nearly eight million shares owned by Service Corp. As a result of that offering, Service Corp no longer has any ownership or financial interest in Equity Corp.</p>
<p>Service Corp's first quarter ends March 31.</p>
